{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"628470-old-woman-in-a-bottle","title":"Jigen Magett Bi Sii Butail Bii","description":"Magett bu doiluyut dem deka sey butail  bena biss am amm Luko setisey  purr ham luhewl. ","language":"Wolof","langCode":"wo","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Isatou Fofana"],"illustrators":["Abraham Muzee"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/628470-old-woman-in-a-bottle"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/418464/size3/5e97aa42c6ae04ac3e506a40327ad23e.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/418464/size6/5e97aa42c6ae04ac3e506a40327ad23e.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415423/size6/2abca3aabce865594553994fc1dbc740.jpg","text":"Dafa amon gijen bu magett bu dekon sii butail mom kenna. Dii jambatu sayuu neka.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415424/size6/0a4172622732b84f25b472baeb587a83.jpg","text":"Bena bess mu'am luu rawbaa sii borii keeram muu gess ko mugi saigam.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415426/size6/83ddabcb51610874a8f0cf93a3b5a6a1.jpg","text":"Lolu tahaw laako \"luhewl luu tah gaagii saagam.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415427/size6/4d2b3ee8cf34fe51dcb961d157424513.jpg","text":"Dama sonna dii daka sey birii butail ,\" laa ko magett bii tontu.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415428/size6/f94b9261558ac7bc01a17b33abeb4142.jpg","text":"Lolu nekko,\" jogal, taslu saa loho yee nyarii yown, gaa olbataiku nyatii yown\".","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415430/size6/c1782938824360090afe0ff0909e6099.jpg","text":"Bum defee lum ko wah mu defee, gijen bu magett bii giss bopam sey nake bu eme.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415431/size6/e1bb0b93ee26f7b6f30f330e939c5351.jpg","text":"Aiy fan sey kanam lolu nyowateh faa wyaa dafaa feka magett bii mugi sagem att.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415432/size6/299ecdff48480b7f1704998179aea8e4.jpg","text":"Lolu lajatiko,\" lu hewl? Lutaa gai sagame?\"","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415433/size6/f39b4c07bc68c50428c7db9b7c3e7abd.jpg","text":"Neike bii dafa tuti. Bugumako,\" laa ko magett bi tontu.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415434/size6/0151b179d3480e68f7c56d8d431089cf.jpg","text":"Lolu nekko, \" jugal, gaa taslu saa loho nyarii yown, gaa wondelu nyatiee yown\".","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415435/size6/5ce6a3f18ac45d56db12ed33187c5e99.jpg","text":"Bum defee lum ko wah, gijen bu magett gess bopam syee nakei bu reey.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415437/size6/b6d5e767c65544ef2059aaa5c38f5a13.jpg","text":"Lolu nyowateh purr Setsey gijen bu magett bii atti. Mu fekako ben tai contan nut tei nahari dehret.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415438/size6/d4bd3b729d684f71c16272a91e8cc9b5.jpg","text":"Lolu lajatiko luhewl magett?\" Magett bii tontu ko, \"nake bii dafe lendem teh teelem.\"","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415439/size6/55614f9211edd1b85ceab64f4bd13710.jpg","text":"Lolu nekko, \"jogal gaa taslu saa loho nyarii yown,\nwindeyluu nyitee yown.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415440/size6/7ac6f863f964640530e59a7ca41cb9dd.jpg","text":"Bum defee lum ko wah, magett giss sati bopam sey butail bi.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/415441/size6/0340fc60fbe0239eadc1a42af31a0737.jpg","text":"Gijen nii magett gess sut jama jum aam. Mom ko dalow wateh sey butail, ak naharr.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":211}}